query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, c.name AS category_name
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.categoryId = c.id
WHERE p.name LIKE '%命理%' OR p.name LIKE '%祈福%' OR p.name LIKE '%Fortune%' OR p.name LIKE '%Prayer%'
ORDER BY p.id;
